OL,3,CUnite suspends Angela Rayner over
OL,4,CBirmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FUnite, one of the largest trade unions
OL,7,Fin the UK, has suspended Angela
OL,8,FRayner's membership over the
OL,9,FBirmingham bin strikes row.
OL,11,FIt also voted to "re-examine its
OL,12,Frelationship" with Labour over the
OL,13,Fissue, in a sign of growing divide
OL,14,Fbetween the union and the party who
OL,15,Fhave historically worked hand-in-hand.
