OL,3,CUnite suspends Angela Rayner over
OL,4,CBirmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FThe announcement comes after a vote by
OL,7,FUnite members at their conference in
OL,8,FBrighton, where they condemned the
OL,9,FLabour-run council in Birmingham, and
OL,10,Fthe government, for "attacking the bin
OL,11,Fworkers".
OL,13,FHowever, sources told ITV News that
OL,14,FRayner is no longer a member of the
OL,15,Funion, after resigning her membership
OL,16,Fsome months ago.
OL,18,FUnite sources insist their membership
OL,19,Fsystem shows she is still an active
OL,20,Fmember and she did not formally resign.
