OL,6,FThe union said fire and rehire tactics
OL,7,Fhad "effectively" been deployed
OL,8,Fagainst striking workers, who are
OL,9,Ftaking industrial action in a dispute
OL,10,Fover pay and job conditions which has
OL,11,Fbeen ongoing for four months.
OL,13,FUnite General Secretary Sharon Graham
OL,14,Fsaid: "Unite is crystal clear it will
OL,15,Fcall out bad employers regardless of
OL,16,Fthe colour of their rosette.
