OL,6,F"Angela Rayner has had every
OL,7,Fopportunity to intervene and resolve
OL,8,Fthis dispute but has instead backed a
OL,9,Frogue council that has peddled lies
OL,10,Fand smeared its workers fighting huge
OL,11,Fpay cuts.
OL,13,F"The disgraceful actions of the
OL,14,Fgovernment and a so-called Labour
OL,15,Fcouncil, is essentially fire and
OL,16,Frehire and makes a joke of the
OL,17,FEmployment Relations Act promises.
