OL,3,CUnite suspends Angela Rayner over
OL,4,CBirmingham bin strikes
OL,6,F"People up and down the country are
OL,7,Fasking whose side is the Labour
OL,8,Fgovernment on and coming up with the
OL,9,Fanswer not workers."
OL,11,FUnite is listed as an affiliated union
OL,12,Fof the Labour Party. Last year, it
OL,13,Foffered the most financial support out
OL,14,Fof all 11 affiliated unions to Labour
OL,15,FMPs.
OL,17,FIn 2024, it gave more than #500,000 in
OL,18,Fthe run up to the election including
OL,19,F#10,000 to Rayner herself, according
OL,20,Fto the Parliamentary Register of
OL,21,FMembers' Financial Interests.
