OL,6,FA Downing Street spokesman said the
OL,7,Fgovernment's priority throughout the
OL,8,Fdispute had "always" been Birmingham's
OL,9,Fresidents.
OL,11,FThe No 10 spokesman also told
OL,12,Freporters: "As you know, Unite's
OL,13,Findustrial action caused disruption to
OL,14,Fwaste collection.
OL,16,F"We have worked intensively with the
OL,17,Fcouncil to tackle the backlog and
OL,18,Fclean up the streets for the residents
OL,19,Ffor public health.
