OL,6,F"We remain in close contact with the
OL,7,Fcouncil and continue to monitor the
OL,8,Fsituation as we support its recovery
OL,9,Fand transformation.
OL,11,F"I think it's important to look back
OL,12,Fto the context of this dispute: Unite
OL,13,Fis in dispute against Birmingham City
OL,14,FCouncil's decision to reform unfair
OL,15,Fstaff structures, which were a major
OL,16,Fcause of unequal pay claims and left
OL,17,Fthe council liable to hundreds of
OL,18,Fmillions of pounds in claims, and that
OL,19,Fwas a key factor cited in the council
OL,20,Fsection 114 notice in 2023, declaring
OL,21,Fbankruptcy."
